description:
House Rules Series 3 Episode 3

The teams have just under two days to bring some sparkle to a rough diamond in the northern suburbs of Melbourne. The pressure to finish on time is overwhelming - on top of that is the desire to do a good job for home owners, Bronik and Corrine. As the site unleashes mayhem, will this be the first unfinished home in House Rules history?
